      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EXTRAVAGANTLY (5) found some support last start but struggled into fourth (23.73), beaten 6 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Has ability and looks hard to stop. ROUGH BOY ROCKY (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 305m behind Compton Ava (18.06) in a TG1-4W. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Cannot be left out. COMPTON ZIRCONIA (8) continues to race well, filling the minors at the last three starts, the latest at this track in 23.61. Tends to go well on this box draw. Will go close here with a clear run. NULLA DANNY BOY (2) is likely to have admirers.",
